event_key.description: A struct that represents a globally unique id for an Event stream that a user can listen to. By design, the lower part of EventKey is the same as account address.

anyOf.description: Indicates an error from the VM, e.g. OUT_OF_GAS, INVALID_AUTH_KEY, RET_TYPE_MISMATCH_ERROR etc. The code will neither EXECUTED nor ABORTED
Indicates an `abort` from inside Move code. Contains the location of the abort and the code
Indicates an failure from inside Move code, where the VM could not continue exection, e.g. dividing by zero or a missing resource
